<div class="hello-im-mike mb-5">
  <p class="lead text-center">Hello! I'm a web developer from Berkshire UK.<br>I've specialised in making performant Ruby on Rails applications since 2012.</p>
  <div class="text-center mt-4 mb-3">
    <a href="mailto:me+site@mikerogers.io?subject=Work%20with%20You" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Me via Email</a>
  </div>
</div>

